    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>- ARE YOU READY FOR HOT SEAT? -</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035810/extras/c9f6883e26244f93d8a7e5be32358d75.poster.avif?t=1747852891\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035810/extras/c9f6883e26244f93d8a7e5be32358d75.webm?t=1747852891\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035810/extras/c9f6883e26244f93d8a7e5be32358d75.mp4?t=1747852891\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><i>Welcome to <strong>Vulkan</strong> Computing Security Systems.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i> </i><br><i>Here at <strong>Vulkan</strong>, we strive to build better condor systems, to allow the world a smoother trip through the virtual realm.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035810/extras/9b6d0d2001a560db1de2c0db9e844b6b.poster.avif?t=1747852891\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035810/extras/9b6d0d2001a560db1de2c0db9e844b6b.webm?t=1747852891\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035810/extras/9b6d0d2001a560db1de2c0db9e844b6b.mp4?t=1747852891\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Its only the dark right?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035810/extras/149b67342370cdcf4e9fefe51a5a1ae0.poster.avif?t=1747852891\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035810/extras/149b67342370cdcf4e9fefe51a5a1ae0.webm?t=1747852891\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035810/extras/149b67342370cdcf4e9fefe51a5a1ae0.mp4?t=1747852891\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>We are looking to appoint a brand-new IT Technician to join the <strong>Vulkan</strong> team, to help with maintaining and updating the computing systems at the high security facility ‘QUASAR’©.</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035810/extras/3a41efe02977530464f961a66b5cbf0e.poster.avif?t=1747852891\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035810/extras/3a41efe02977530464f961a66b5cbf0e.webm?t=1747852891\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035810/extras/3a41efe02977530464f961a66b5cbf0e.mp4?t=1747852891\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>DISCLAIMER: During your shifts you are responsible for the monitoring and documentation of highly dangerous subject and high security assets. We are not liable for any injuries including: mental trauma, loss of limbs, or death.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Chapter 1 is just the beginning! We hope to build new chapters every 6/9 months!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035810/extras/7476114fdbc521974df6ffa1c0d55